{"tid":2222661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「言語平息暴力」美選辯論前夕　拜登獲諾貝爾和平獎提名","createTime":"2020-09-29T08:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T11:51:23.000Z","uid":231908,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b888ccc24961bba27d3f863f0492508850cec95f","tid":2222661,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"2020年諾貝爾獎即將於10月5日至12日公布得獎名單，日前曾有消息傳出，美國總統川普被提名諾貝爾和平獎，然而就在美國總統大選進入白熱化的此刻，有外媒報導，民主黨候選人拜登也同樣獲得提名，提名人則是英國工黨議員克里斯布萊恩（Chris Bryant）。<br />\n<br />\n根據英媒《天空新聞台》報導，美國總統大選民主黨候選人拜登（Joe Biden）已獲得諾貝爾和平獎的提名，有望與川普共同角逐此項殊榮。提名拜登的正是英國反對黨工黨議員克里斯布萊恩，布萊恩認為，當全美陷入暴力抗議中，拜登靠著自己的影響力緩解了全國的緊張局勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/joe-biden-nobel-peace-prize-1534802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fjoe-biden-nobel-peace-prize-1534802&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=b936ebb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsweek.com/joe-biden-nobel-peace-prize-1534802</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/baseballot/status/1310573983239155712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbaseballot%2Fstatus%2F1310573983239155712&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=fd52d6d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbaseballot%2Fstatus%2F1310573983239155712&h=f545352c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/baseballot/status/1310573983239155712</a>"},{"pid":"ef540e6e16d3f384dff9eedd9a5c57ddda7fd67f","tid":2222661,"uid":62532,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"make Love <span class=\"pink\">with children</span><br />\nno war"},{"pid":"9022bdaa1b2a747e95f98eaddc12b523715c0ada","tid":2222661,"uid":52043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾性騷擾女童獎就有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1e377b6e11d166b0ee8d81855fb946427611a8","